  "content": "<div><br></div>\n<div><font face=\".AppleColorEmojiUI\">📜</font> Certain characters now have the ability to “reroll” the class setting, altering the lens through which the material is analyzed.</div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div><font face=\"ZapfDingbatsITC\">✔</font> If a student uses a “Realm Reroll,” the class moves to a different setting &amp shifts analytical filters.</div>\n<div><font face=\"ZapfDingbatsITC\">✔</font> The character who initiated the shift gains a temporary advantage.</div>\n<div><font face=\"ZapfDingbatsITC\">✔</font> New rules &amp filters apply depending on the setting.</div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div>Example: Week 5 – Modernism</div>\n<div><br></div>\n<div><object><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse: collapse; direction: ltr\">\n<tbody>\n<tr><td valign=\"top\" style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px; border-color: #ccc; padding: 3.0px 5.0px 3.0px 5.0px; min-width: 70px\"><div>Original Setting</div>\n</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px; border-color: #ccc; padding: 3.0px 5.0px 3.0px 5.0px; min-width: 70px\"><div>Rerolled Setting</div>\n</td><td valign=\"top\" style=\"border-style: solid; border-width: 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px 1.0px; border-color: #ccc; padding: 3.0px 5.0px 3.0px 5.0px; min-width: 70px\"><div>Effect</div>",
